race.comment: THEBUDGIESMUGLA (2) lightly raced stayer who looks to be heading in the right direction. Stalked the speed when up in trip and grade for a sharp victory over 2400m here at this level. Looks to have a stack of upside and can go on with it again. PRESLEY (10) coming along slowly and meets a few of these better at the weights today. Out to the 2000m at his second run back when fav, for a respectable fourth with the 59kg at Hawkesbury. Kept fresh and shapes as a solid top three prospect. CAPTAIN MAVERICK (3) dour on-pace stayer due for a change of luck. Gunned down late with the 60kg when a fighting second over 2100m at Warwick Farm. Likely to roll forward with the in form Rawiller engaged. Should handle the rise in trip. WAR RIBBON (6) three runs back have been excellent and set to peak today after sticking on gamely when second over 2400m here at latest. Adept in all conditions and can overcome the sticky draw. CLAIM THE CROWN (4) frustrating gelding with slim place claims.
